                        <interp inst="t18351123-name-566" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL BROOKS</persName>
                  </hi>. I went to Mr. Orlemann, and found the prisoner there, selling these guts—he was going to have 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. for them; but he had made them dirty by drawing them over the tiles, and Mr. Orlemann would not have them—this is my own pail—It is my own mending, and what I had left in the factory.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
